item.title: New version of Tracer - Tracer v1.6 - now available!
item.description: OK, heads up everyone using BEAST, or interested in summarizing and analyzing the results of Bayesian analyses in other software programs! There is a new version of the program Tracer available at Andrew Rambaut’s website. You can obtain the new version of Tracer, Tracer v1.6 by downloading the appropriate version here.
